# Database backups
/backups

# Claude Code local state — but framework-distributed skills under
# .claude/skills/ are checked in (they're versioned content from the
# Metasession SDLC, not developer-local).
# Use .claude/* (not .claude/) so the negation below can re-include skills/.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
